      • executeSPR

        public SPRRuntime executeSPR(SPR sprToExecute)
        Description copied from interface: ISPRExecutor
        Sends the specified SPR for execution to Sunrise controller.

        Returns directly after sending SPR to controller. Do not waits or checks whether the SPR was accepted.
        All information about the execution of the SPR including states etc can be get from the returned SPRRuntime

        Specified by:
        executeSPR in interface ISPRExecutor
        Parameters:
        sprToExecute - SPR to execute
        Returns:
        runtime object containing execution information of the specified SPR
